Name: Wallet Audubon Birds
Description: No International Shipping!/video below/Tweet this! Stuck inside and missing the great outdoors? Now you can turn anyplace into a bird(call) sanctuary! The Audubon Birds wallet features beautiful paintings by John James Audubon, the great artist and ornithologist and a dozen bird calls and birdsongs. If you cover the wallet's light sensor, the wallet stays quiet. But if you uncover the sensor, every time you open the wallet you'll get to hear:American Robin Blue Jay Canada WarblerIndigo Bunting Mourning DoveNorthern Cardinal Summer Tanager Warbling Vireo White-throated SparrowWood Thrush This wallet makes a perfect gift for bird-watchers, nature-lovers, people who like to prank their cats, or any of your fine, feathered friends. Made of durable TyvekВ®

Includes a silencer if you'd rather have your money do the talking. Made of durable TyvekВ®.
